am\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Jiu-Jitsu_No-Gi_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pan-American champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Jiu-Jitsu_No-Gi_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Jiu-Jitsu_No-Gi_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her win, Phogat seals a medal finish for India, and also becomes the first Indian female wrestler to compete for Gold in an Olympic final.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9900082325041939, \"rank\": 0.005190879086867155, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8661618227439047, \"rank\": 0.15351287129006164, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both wrestlers started off the bout patiently, grappling away at each other, but playing it slow and safe as to not give away any cheap points early.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, around a minute into the bout, Phogat finally found the breakthrough, taking down the Cuban Guzman, but could not seal any points.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"score\": 0.9925557733975595, \"rank\": 0.007441084514443992, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo engaged in a grapplefest, as Guzman was hit with a 30-sec shotclock for passivity, through which Vinesh held her ground to secure the first point of the match.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guzman continued to target Phogat's legs, but neither the Cuban nor the Indian found any leeway to snatch away points, as both wrestlers went into the halfway break with Phogat leading 1-0.\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"score\": 0.9925557733975595, \"rank\": 0.007441084514443992, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\"}, {\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8661618227439047, \"rank\": 0.15351287129006164, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Entering into action in the remainder of the time, Phogat was hit with a passivity shotclock herself.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But unlike Guzman, Phogat exploded pinning away the Cuban at will to snatch away 4 more points, building up her lead to 5-0 with less than a minute to go.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"score\": 0.9925557733975595, \"rank\": 0.007441084514443992, \"text\": \